  "3054550": {
    "name": "Sil与消逝之境",
    "steam_appid": 3054550,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/f79f889c49387f9ef4e8d28e600c3321.avif?t=1770201746\" width=585 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/01c1fe96db47441ed8c095bf801be7a7.webp?t=1770201746\" width=1170 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独自挑战 MMO 团队副本级首领！在被远古下界诸神摧残的黑暗世界—阿里塔斯中，揭开你的过往。本作是一款动作角色扮演游戏（ARPG），拥有 9 大职业专精、数百件独特装备、海量技能、复杂的角色养成体系，以及激烈的团队副本级首领战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/35d2da6ebcc57e681688780f454ec377.poster.avif?t=1770201746\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/35d2da6ebcc57e681688780f454ec377.webm?t=1770201746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/35d2da6ebcc57e681688780f454ec377.mp4?t=1770201746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/9d852286c7f351f3ddf9f18d1a23e16e.avif?t=1770201746\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/01c1fe96db47441ed8c095bf801be7a7.webp?t=1770201746\" width=1170 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>9 大独特职业专精</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以三大基础职业之一开启你的旅程，每个职业都有完全不同的玩法。随着冒险深入，你将解锁更高阶的专精，拓展技能树与战略选择，进一步打磨你的流派构筑。<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>110+ 传奇与传家宝装备</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用海量魔法装备武装自己，并通过锻造不断强化。传奇与传家宝装备不仅能大幅增强角色，更能彻底改变你的玩法思路。深度随机掉落系统保证你总能保持动力，永远追寻下一个关键升级。<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无数独特技能与亲和效果</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索多样化的技能，每个技能都拥有不同的亲和效果，可强化、改造甚至彻底重塑你的战斗风格。让你的【血色斩击】化为血之漩涡撕裂敌群，把【地裂重击】转化为吞没战场的火山喷发，或召唤【基特拉】的幻影分身来向敌人传播剧毒！<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>寻找你的命运</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在世界各地寻找陨落英雄的墓地，继承他们的力量，铸就属于你的宿命。200+ 命运节点任你自由组合，打造出最契合你玩法的独特构筑！<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强大的遗物与灵魂水晶</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驭远古遗物之力，镶嵌蕴含首领与怪物精华的灵魂水晶。利用这些水晶放大你的流派，将敌人的力量反过来为你所用！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/07acee8ee42d67a6f0d2debcf007c92c.poster.avif?t=1770201746\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/07acee8ee42d67a6f0d2debcf007c92c.webm?t=1770201746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/07acee8ee42d67a6f0d2debcf007c92c.mp4?t=1770201746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快节奏、流畅的第三人称战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过全新视角碾压成群敌人，享受畅快的近战体验。打击感十足的视觉与音效强化了每一次挥砍的重量，同时保持顺滑的移动与灵活的镜头操作。<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索阿里塔斯</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开阿里塔斯的秘密，阻止“下界之人”蔓延的腐化！帮助村民、追寻自己的过往，在 30+ 主线与支线任务中对抗史诗级首领。每个角落都潜藏新的惊喜！<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战诸神</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直面最强大的怪物，在史诗级首领战中检验你的流派构筑。这是对你实力与反应力的终极考验。<br>    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无尽可重玩的团队副本式终局内容</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在无尽的终局副本中不断前进，完善你的构筑，挑战纯净形态的化身首领。唯有最强韧的流派方能胜出，获取专属的“纯净物品”。突破极限，没有上限！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/315bbc3f67451d79a69920551f2d3a06.poster.avif?t=1770201746\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/315bbc3f67451d79a69920551f2d3a06.webm?t=1770201746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/315bbc3f67451d79a69920551f2d3a06.mp4?t=1770201746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/01c1fe96db47441ed8c095bf801be7a7.webp?t=1770201746\" width=1170 height=42 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/b46c8c08e3a37249ce0f09f81a9e3338.poster.avif?t=1770201746\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/b46c8c08e3a37249ce0f09f81a9e3338.webm?t=1770201746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054550/extras/b46c8c08e3a37249ce0f09f81a9e3338.mp4?t=1770201746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
